[32m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### detailed_summary                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I attempted to test the `/convert` endpoint for SSRF vulnerability by        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m sending POST requests with various localhost variations (localhost,          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 127.0.0.1, 0.0.0.0, [::1]) targeting the `/admin` endpoint. All requests     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m consistently returned the same error message: "Either URL or Markdown text   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m is required!"                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Multiple approaches were tested:                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Sending `url` parameter with localhost variations                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Sending `markdown_text` parameter alone                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Sending URL-encoded values                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Sending both parameters together                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Using different formats and encodings                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m All attempts resulted in HTTP 302 redirects back to the homepage with a      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m flash message indicating the validation failure. The server appears to be    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m rejecting all form submissions, suggesting:                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The Playwright tool may not be properly sending the POST body data in a    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m format Flask can parse                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - There may be additional validation (CSRF tokens, referrer checks, or other [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m protections)                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The form data might need to be submitted through an actual browser context [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m with session/cookies                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The GET request to the homepage worked successfully, confirming the server   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m is accessible. However, none of the POST requests to `/convert` were         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m accepted, preventing the SSRF test from being executed.                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ###proofs                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Successful GET Request:**                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m GET / HTTP/1.1                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Host: 127.0.0.1:32810                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Response: HTTP/1.1 200 OK                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Failed POST Attempts (all variations):**                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m POST /convert HTTP/1.1                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Host: 127.0.0.1:32810                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Content-Length: 32                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m url=http://localhost:32810/admin                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Response: HTTP/1.1 302 FOUND                                                 [32m│[0m
